title: Fully furnished one bedroom apartment include utilities
description: The units offer expansive closet space and storage. The complex has recently undergone renovations and features newly updated apartments, balconies, windows, and common areas as well as a pool and fitness center. East Shore apartments are situated at the east end of the city on or near the attractive Wampanoag Trail which leads to the affluent towns of Barrington and Bristol and Rhode Island's picturesque inner coast. Heat & Hot Water are included in rent.

Today I am going to share with you 3 things you MUST know if you are looking to buy your first home and stop paying high rent this year (Watch out for #3, Almost everyone get's it wrong).

1.)In most cases you will NOT need 10% or even 20% down! In Rhode Island we have many First time home buyer programs that allow you to buy your first home with low money down as low as even 0% down...
The $7,500 First Time Home Buyers assistance program just came back in Rhode Island! It is now statewide!
2.) If your credit needs work call us anyway. We will do what we can to work with you and help you get pre-approved over time.

3.) You can work with one of our buyers agents for no charge. Your buyers agent will help you find the perfect home, negotiate price and conditions with the seller, and walk you through the entire home buying process from start to finish.
Many renters come to us with the dream of home ownership. We have helped many people become happy first time home owners. Click here to see some of our recent reviews.
If you have any questions feel free to reach out!

title: ❄Fully Remodeled Townhome!❄
description: Our apartments are designed for real living. Our open kitchens include a refrigerator, dishwasher, and a gas stove. The kitchen has been recently updated with pine cabinets and modern granite countertops.  We have wall-to-wall carpeting in the living room and bedrooms, the master has an impressive closet for all your storage needs.

Walk right into your apartment to a tiled foyer with a coat closet at the entry. The living space has impressive plank flooring throughout. Each Townhome has individually-controlled heat and built-in air conditioning.

Beyond the walls of your apartment you can delight in scenic walk at Rose Larisa Park or enjoy the historic Crescent Carousal. With easy highway access for commuting to work or to enjoy what Providence has to offer, there’s so much to do, it's hard to know where to begin!
Call to schedule a tour today!

title: Fully furnished one bedroom apartment include utilities
description: The units offer expansive closet space and storage. The complex has recently undergone renovations and features newly updated apartments, balconies, windows, and common areas as well as a pool and fitness center. Just miles from Providence, East Providence is a city unto itself with a wide range of neighborhoods, commercial and retail areas. East Shore apartments are situated at the east end of the city on or near the attractive Wampanoag Trail which leads to the affluent towns of Barrington and Bristol and Rhode Island's picturesque inner coast. Heat & Hot Water are included in rent.

title: Vaulted ceilings, 66 acres of extensive lush landscaping, Dog park

Silver Spring Golf course and East Bay Bike Path are just seconds from your home. Winchester Park & Woods offers 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartment homes and great amenities such as an outdoor Swimming Pool, Tennis Court, state of the art Fitness Area, Playground and Dog Park! Pets are welcome! Come see what we have to offer, you will love your new home!
